name: Science Bowl
description: Participate in a competitive math and science competition involving a variety of subjects including the latest information from the U.S. National Labs. Sponsored by the DOE. This is another club that allows students to explore science besides SciOly. Open to 9th, 10th, 11th, 12th grade students.

announcements.title: Meetings
announcements.description: Club meetings take place Fridays 3:30 to 4:35 at room 281. Club Fee more than $10.
